name: Lin Zhiling 志玲姐姐
description:
这是我第三个训练的模型，基本上没多大进步，我的显卡现存也少，所以估计是没什么进步空间了。
请不要用它生成NSFW的图片，不要做出侵权的行为，如果需要我也会下架这个模型。
另外，用它生成上半身图已经是极限了，脸部在图中占比越小，效果越差。虽然我在训练图集中已经加入了一些全身和半身照片，但似乎并没有太大用处。我没有别的使用建议了，因为我自己也不是太懂如何生成比较完美的图。

This is my third trained model. Basically, there is not much progress. My current graphics card has limited memory. So I guess there is little room for progress.
Please do not use it to generate NSFW images or infringing actions. I will also take down this model if necessary.
In addition, generating upper body images is the limit. The smaller the face in the picture, the worse the effect. Although I have added some full body and half body photos in the training set, it doesn't seem to be much use. I have no other usage suggestions because I don't understand well how to generate perfect pictures myself.
